        "main_text": "<h3>How it works…<\/h3><p>Artistic skill might come naturally or develop over time, but nothing should get in the way of creative expression or achieving authentic results. You just need the right tools and the right know-how.<\/p><p>Art markers aren’t like normal colouring pens, they apply perfectly smoothly and will layer and blend for an array of versatile effects. This is why they are so widely used by professional creatives within the comic, movie and gaming industries.<\/p><p>By combining with officially licensed character designs on premium paper, plus expert instruction and pro-tips, you’ve got everything you need to immerse in your fandom and create without limits!  <\/p>",
